name: DeFido
description: DeFido is the adorable French Bulldog mascot of Coinbase, and it's on a mission to support Coinbase's vision of bringing people onto the blockchain through the power of community. We firmly believe that DeFido is the brand best suited to bolster BASE's growth and cultivate a vibrant, all-embracing community that supports the BASE chain's ascent to the top. Just as its counterparts have played crucial roles in propelling other chains to greatness, DeFido is here to champion BASE and make it a leading force in the blockchain landscape.
